name: Rocket Cat
description:
For some reason most of the sound effects and the music don't work on safari but they do on chrome. 

On Ios safari only the meow sfx works and you can't stop the music from playing. would love feedback on how to fix and how it works on other browsers and on android. :)

Collect garbage to build the highest tower. Press Space or Tap to jump to avoid people. Once you use up all your materials you can shoot your tower with a missile
